{"tid":2092146,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新任國安公署署長曾於烏坎事件批評村民找外媒出頭","createTime":"2020-07-03T05:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T05:36:32.000Z","uid":60281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2f0c38c6a826042fdfe8738fca3d5d8df5390099","tid":2092146,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:22:10.000Z","msg":"烏坎村<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國務院任命鄭雁雄為中央駐港國安公署署長。今年57歲的鄭雁雄是廣東汕頭人，2005年至2013年期間在汕尾市任職，曾經擔任市委副書記、政法委書記、市委書記等多個職務。<br />\n<br />\n鄭雁雄2011年擔任汕尾市委書記期間，烏坎村村民曾發生土地維權事件，當時一名村民被當局拘留期間猝死，觸發大規模抗爭。鄭雁雄其後指，村民表達訴求有好的初衷，但用了錯誤方法，有境外勢力更推波助瀾，導致已經平息的事件再趨嚴重。網上曾流傳片段，他在一次内部會議上，形容「境外媒體信得過，母豬都會上樹」，批評村民找境外傳媒出頭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535584-20200703.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535584-20200703.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXPvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=68c3223b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535584-20200703.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dc0ba367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535584-20200703.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3b87468162fe2ccddf3d60cd282e9f7244538102","tid":2092146,"uid":24788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:25:54.000Z","msg":"管開汕尾<br />\n依家來管香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑死人咩"},{"pid":"ec71c74df0451aeb7ccd7c225218c6f497fa4b70","tid":2092146,"uid":52760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZJaf62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZJaf62.png&h=e3fe7391&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年講境外媒體係唔係指白粉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fd9270527b8f342c0885a4f737